entries.text: Hello, I'm having trouble logging into my account. My name is Alice Smith.
I can help with that, Alice. Can you confirm the email address associated with your account and a contact phone number?
Yes, my email is alice.smith@example.com and my phone number is +1-202-555-0100.
Thank you, Alice. I'm looking up your account now. Please bear with me for a moment.
Okay, I see an account under that email. It seems there was a temporary lock. I've reset your password and sent a new one to your email. Please check your inbox.
Got it! I've received the email and successfully logged in. Thank you so much for your quick assistance!
